keyMappings:
map <c-x>k removeTab
map <c-x>b restoreTab
map <a-h> previousTab
map <a-l> nextTab
unmap J
unmap K
unmap gt
unmap gT
map <a-H> moveTabLeft
map <a-L> moveTabRight
map <c-v> scrollFullPageDown
map <a-v> scrollFullPageUp
map <c-i> focusInput
unmap p
unmap P
unmap m
unmap `
map m toggleMuteTab
unmap d
unmap u
map <c-d> scrollPageDown
map <c-u> scrollPageUp
map e Vomnibar.activateEditUrl
map E Vomnibar.activateEditUrlInNewTab
map <c-f> LinkHints.activateModeWithQueue
unmap <a-f>
map <a-f> LinkHints.activateModeToOpenIncognito
map p passNextKey
